    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "Licence To Grill",
        "Description": "&quot;This is no place for you, Diana. Go home.&quot;\r\r&quot;Oh, don&apos;t be an idiot, 47. I know exactly what you&apos;re up to, and quite frankly, you&apos;re going to need my help. Remember, if it hadn&apos;t been for my Branch, you&apos;d have failed long ago.&quot;\r\r    [opens a briefcase]\r\r&quot;Everything for a man on holiday. A Gas Canister - guaranteed to grill someone to perfection and a Kukri Machete - It might prove effective in the jungle - or otherwise.&quot;\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as YupItsPurple.",
